{"tid":2460924,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(not)是日靚午 酸菜魚","createTime":"2021-03-25T06:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T12:12:15.000Z","uid":111088,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e4f4bd7fb0e66ae0193ed73eee1084780dd98f","tid":2460924,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVh2T1ZCJLGG1T6eA6VDi1u5NTC147vpqcSGpSXMkwCef?filename=0jgAYAT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jgAYAT.jpg&h=dc4c4846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個真心巴閉<br />\n平時食嗰啲酸菜魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n菜多過魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲魚又薄又鞋仲要周不時食到碎骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻得嚟又唔夠香辣得嚟又唔夠層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個就唔同呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢用嘅魚又靚，似係厚肉鱸魚唔係奀滋滋薄片草魚<br />\n佢又片得厚肉得嚟又入味又夠滑又夠鮮<br />\n跟住仲有啲花椒<br />\n佢用曬青紅花椒<br />\n成件事個層次即刻提升左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有佢下面有啲薯粉<br />\n又滑又煙韌又掛湯又順口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個湯又唔會太酸但係又夠鮮夠酸夠味夠開胃<br />\n飲完唔會渴<br />\n本雀誠意推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af6cb247fc1ec5ec54a6bc3e8b459a320d9e6b8","tid":2460924,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:41:33.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"41a2e7dd083c64c95dfb1ad0e62af0a0acd6ca17","tid":2460924,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:47:33.000Z","msg":"魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d03a0ff24c99b9e6d363021d8d2bc9005b7ffe5","tid":2460924,"uid":43647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"b62dc52fd2b1684afe031bafb8dd3aede4fffcc1","tid":2460924,"uid":149833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"真係幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊間？幾多人份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fe5b3a0980deb9d25a0ad0dea04834554af16a","tid":2460924,"uid":111088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b62dc52fd2b1684afe031bafb8dd3aede4fffcc1","tid":2460924,"uid":149833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"真係幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊間？幾多人份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:19:36.000Z","msg":"我同個fd兩個人都食到好飽"},{"pid":"abbd2b8b315dbbc0e9c70ccd9e0c823f5ad4df02","tid":2460924,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d03a0ff24c99b9e6d363021d8d2bc9005b7ffe5","tid":2460924,"uid":43647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:55:33.000Z","m